# 1Ô∏è‚É£5Ô∏è‚É£ OBJECTIVITY & BIAS CONTROLS

System prevents:

* Personal retaliation scoring
* Score manipulation
* Non-evidence-based evaluation
* Unjustified extreme ratings

Controls include:

* Mandatory justification text
* Supporting documentation upload
* Multi-reviewer validation
* Weighted scoring formula
* Audit traceability

